node.text:
The new BUGATTI smartwatch range, created with VIITA Watches, mirrors the unrivalled precision, artistry and technology synonymous with hyper sports cars crafted in Molsheim. Each of the models offers an innumerable amount of technical features and is built by hand with meticulous attention to detail for a seamless integration of more than 1,000 individual parts. Discover the collection at www.bugatti.com or www.bugatti-smartwatches.com. @bugatti_smartwatches

#BUGATTI #BUGATTILifestyle #BUGATTISmartwatches #VIITA #VIITAforBUGATTI #VIITAWatches

node.text: No other driver spends more time in a BUGATTI CHIRON than he does: Andy Wallace. In the last few years, the Englishman and Pilote Officiel covered a total of over 150,000 km in the hyper sports cars from Molsheim. He thus is the perfect person to show owners and fans how to make the most of this unique vehicle. In a series of five video clips, Andy explains the car’s technical details in a comprehensible manner and reveals what the CHIRON is capable of and still driving it safely. Fasten your seatbelts! #BUGATTI #Chiron #AndyWallace

node.text: No other driver spends more time in a BUGATTI CHIRON than he does: Andy Wallace. In the last few years, the Englishman and Pilote Officiel covered a total of over 150,000 km in the hyper sports cars from Molsheim. He thus is the perfect person to show owners and fans how to make the most of this unique vehicle. In a series of five video clips, Andy explains the car’s technical details in a comprehensible manner and reveals what the CHIRON is capable of and still driving it safely. Fasten your seatbelts! #BUGATTI #Chiron #AndyWallace

There are few cities that match the CHIRON Super Sport’s sheer presence, provenance, and character, but New York City poses worthy competition.

BUGATTI prides itself in the relentless pursuit of engineering perfection, and has continued to do so for more than 110 years. The extreme testing and development process that the CENTODIECI has been subject to is part of achieving this goal. 
 
Subject to hurricane-force winds, the airflow generated inside the wind tunnel envelopes the hyper sports car’s intricate bodywork, so that it can be fine-tuned for optimum aerodynamic performance.
 
Just 10 units of the highly exclusive CENTODIECI will ever be crafted at our Atelier in Molsheim, with deliveries set to begin next year.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTICentodieci #CENTODIECI 
_

The mountain roads around Monaco have been witness to many iconic drives, but every so often, an extraordinary pursuit takes place.

The very first BUGATTI Divo, one of just 40 examples that were ever made, took to the winding and scenic roads to let loose all 1,500 PS. As the pinnacle of modern coachbuilding, the DIVO’s dramatic design and pin-point handling are a perfect fit for the environment.

In tow is the DIVO’s sibling, the CHIRON, to make for stunning duo of engineering prowess.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIDivo #BUGATTIChiron #DIVO #CHIRON
